Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.71,0:00:07.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!\NThere's a city inside the crater!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.92,0:00:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the city of Quon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.34,0:00:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,A flourishing port city famous for being\Na base for drakers.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.55,0:00:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we have lot of repairing to do
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.80,0:00:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,we'll be stationed in this city for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.14,0:00:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,-Yahoo!\N-Good grief...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.85,0:00:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh...! Landing at last.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.27,0:00:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,We had a lot of trouble with the\Nair pirates and everything after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.48,0:00:28.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiro, this is your first time in\Nthis city, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.65,0:00:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.65,0:00:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,This city is a rendezvous point\Nfor a lot of other draking vessels, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.99,0:00:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So diligent as ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.53,0:00:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Our Jiro will be Jiro wherever\Nhe goes, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.91,0:00:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha- What's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.62,0:00:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just that you all are too easy-going.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.66,0:00:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika-san, there! Look, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.20,0:00:43.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Already lookin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.87,0:00:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's land quickly and begin dissecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.88,0:00:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're no fun...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.50,0:00:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika-san, how can you be so dull?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.67,0:00:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after landing
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.55,0:00:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,There's plenty of work for\Ndrakers to keep our hands busy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.84,0:01:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,But, certainly, going to a new place\Nsure gets your heart racing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.60,0:01:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,♪〜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.14,0:02:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,〜♪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.61,0:02:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Let's begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.28,0:02:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.40,0:02:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.82,0:02:43.12,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.24,0:02:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.20,0:02:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Takita!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.83,0:02:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Come over here,\Nlet's see you try your hands at dissecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.25,0:02:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.59,0:02:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't stay "the newbie"\Nforever, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.34,0:02:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ye-... yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.59,0:03:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.43,0:03:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,First, try an horizontal cut\Nin the direction of the tail from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.35,0:03:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.68,0:03:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.68,0:03:10.81,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.14,0:03:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Put more strength into it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.94,0:03:14.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be a scaredy cat!\NDo it in one go! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.98,0:03:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ye-... yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.61,0:03:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.36,0:03:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.74,0:03:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.95,0:03:25.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay... here goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.12,0:03:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.95,0:03:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.58,0:03:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Drive your blade between the meat and the\Nskin to cut it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.08,0:03:34.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So tough...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.63,0:03:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,A little more! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.96,0:03:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.01,0:03:45.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Takita.\NThat was pretty good for your first time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.47,0:03:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go for the red meat now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.76,0:03:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Ye- yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.85,0:03:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.27,0:03:52.19,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.77,0:03:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,At long last!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.35,0:03:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We're done with all the dissecting\Nand deliveries!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.11,0:03:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Finished the clean up too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.98,0:04:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's eat something tasty
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.57,0:04:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,and hit the nearest tavern!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.70,0:04:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.62,0:04:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.78,0:04:08.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're coming with us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.70,0:04:11.54,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.62,0:04:16.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The sensation from the dissection is\Nstill in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.54,0:04:20.09,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.97,0:04:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.80,0:04:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We've sure come a long way...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.76,0:04:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It's done, it's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.10,0:04:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.31,0:04:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.48,0:04:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,If you take into account that she\Nwas still not used to living aboard...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.61,0:04:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Dealt with not only a storm\Nbut air pirates shooting at her as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.57,0:04:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd be pretty overwhelmed\Nby all of that, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.70,0:04:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That girl...\NShe doesn't let her show in her face...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.49,0:04:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm pretty sure that she's been pretty tense.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.99,0:04:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And now that tension has gone off all at once.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.37,0:04:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you sure she's not just hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.50,0:04:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.12,0:04:58.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's during moments like this that\Nnewbies decide to leave the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.67,0:04:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Eehh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.59,0:05:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.55,0:05:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.72,0:05:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.26,0:05:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.85,0:05:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,So tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.19,0:05:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.69,0:05:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You can tell it's different from\Nmeat roasted in a normal skewer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.94,0:05:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, this is roasted after being\Nmarinated in wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.44,0:05:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I was hoping to have these marinate\Novernight but oh well...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.57,0:05:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's why I thought I smelled\Nsomething tasty!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.70,0:05:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The skewers are made from grapevine wood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.74,0:05:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,If you roast meat using these\Nsome of its aroma ends within it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.25,0:05:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika-san, aren't you going out\Nsomewhere today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.12,0:05:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go once I'm done\Neating these.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.00,0:05:42.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Just... wait a moment, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.55,0:05:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.09,0:05:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.55,0:05:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.64,0:05:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you go all-out and changed\Nyour clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.02,0:05:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,A young lady doesn't have the chance\Nto visit a city everyday!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.52,0:06:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If this isn't the moment to wear\Nmy fanciest clothes, then, when is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.03,0:06:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,How about this, young man?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.61,0:06:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,-Wahh!\N-Don't need any.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.65,0:06:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.86,0:06:10.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, come again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.12,0:06:12.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't know you smoked.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.24,0:06:14.20,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.58,0:06:15.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Grrrr!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.29,0:06:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... I'm gonna leave you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.46,0:06:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh... fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.05,0:06:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika-san...\NWhere are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.67,0:06:29.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll arrive soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.64,0:06:33.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A tent?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.56,0:06:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.81,0:06:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.68,0:06:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That smell...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.48,0:06:43.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad...\Nthat you didn't kick the bucket yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.19,0:06:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Gramps Ura.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.15,0:06:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha... I'm also glad you didn't too,\NMika.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.53,0:06:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't see you here\Nfor a month or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.66,0:06:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, it's been 2 or 3 years, gramps.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.45,0:06:56.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh my? Do you have a companion\Nwith you today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.04,0:06:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it is a young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.46,0:07:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Mister, your eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.50,0:07:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.79,0:07:06.50,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you know I was\Na young lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.63,0:07:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I can tell by the smell.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.34,0:07:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,See? Spot on!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.30,0:07:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're too innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.93,0:07:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this old pervert?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.60,0:07:16.81,Default,,0,0,0,,The Thousand Heads Hunter.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.31,0:07:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He is the chief of the clan\Nthat passes down their wisdom\Non how to hunt dragons and dissect them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.85,0:07:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,But now I'm a simple senile\Nold fool, as you can see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.73,0:07:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides that, he always takes\Ncare of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.32,0:07:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.70,0:07:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,They're dragon pelts.\NFrom the dragons we hunted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.20,0:07:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohh... it is pretty well tanned.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.12,0:07:39.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What will be they used for?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.79,0:07:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,To make one of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.00,0:07:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This tent...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.17,0:07:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,It is an ancient tradition...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.00,0:07:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We sew the pelts of the dragons we dissected\Nfor the new generations to inherit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.09,0:07:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Each pattern is different and all of them\Nshare the same meaning: a dragon hunted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.05,0:07:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.18,0:07:59.27,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first dragon I hunted.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.60,0:08:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.93,0:08:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,E-... eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.85,0:08:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Which... means that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.23,0:08:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,All of these patterns\Nrepresent dragons?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.07,0:08:10.69,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.49,0:08:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.95,0:08:14.95,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.24,0:08:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.74,0:08:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Here... it is starting to tear...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.16,0:08:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That one was from 3 generations\Nbefore Gramps Ura.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.58,0:08:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm... I'm touching an ancient dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.25,0:08:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a dragon hunted by\Na famous dissection expert named Ino.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.34,0:08:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,This one was so big that they\Nhad to call people from the neighbouring town.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.35,0:08:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,And even after that,\Nit took seven whole days to dissect.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.01,0:08:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.06,0:08:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But how do you know about all\Nof them, Mika-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.85,0:08:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Gramps Ura told me all the stories\Nand they got stuck in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.10,0:08:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mika used to sit there in front of\Nthat wall without moving for days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.82,0:08:55.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I can understand why he did that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.82,0:08:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Since we have this pelt\Nfrom our most recent dissection...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.66,0:08:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, tan it well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.24,0:09:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That one! That was from the very\Nfirst dragon I dissected!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.33,0:09:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Will it form part of this\Nwall too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.08,0:09:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm... I see, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.88,0:09:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case,\NI think it deserves a very special spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.96,0:09:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Come here, Nanami!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.72,0:09:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The pelt teaches you the way\Nits pattern is gonna be.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.39,0:09:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ohhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.18,0:09:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Its colour, feel, scales and hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.69,0:09:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Its irregularities and scars...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.69,0:09:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You can use all that to form\Nan expression of the pattern by instinct.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.78,0:09:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.41,0:09:39.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-Wanna try?\N-Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.28,0:09:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.74,0:09:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Insert the needle and sew\Nboth sides with the thread while pulling it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.37,0:09:46.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Be careful the needle doesn't get\Nstuck with the thread.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.62,0:09:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dragon's skin tapestry"\NIt's... It's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.75,0:09:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,The stitching is a bit rough\Nand it is a little twisted but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.13,0:09:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I really like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.38,0:09:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.30,0:10:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.85,0:10:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm moved!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.14,0:10:05.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.60,0:10:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That Vanabelle...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.31,0:10:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,She was just hungry\Nas I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.69,0:10:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.65,0:10:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wahh... what a beautiful colour.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.77,0:10:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.53,0:10:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,How does it look?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.28,0:10:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Good old Dag is checking\Nit right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.99,0:10:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The structure and joints seem fine\Nso it seems we only need to replace the plating.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.41,0:10:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the silver lining, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.54,0:10:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Although...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.91,0:10:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,The gains we got this time
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.29,0:10:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,have almost vanished after\Nthe necessary expenses and repair costs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.13,0:10:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,My head hurts so bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.38,0:10:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.34,0:10:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Where are all the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.59,0:10:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone disappeared into\Nthe city quite a while ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.43,0:10:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.93,0:10:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn, what a bunch of slackers.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.51,0:10:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.72,0:10:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well, don't you prefer it this\Nway instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.56,0:10:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we don't have our noisy Takita\Naround after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.98,0:10:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.40,0:10:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's without question.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.77,0:10:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes it is nice to have a drink\Nbetween only us grown-ups.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.19,0:10:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you in?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.19,0:10:59.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I have something special for this ocassion!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.40,0:11:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.61,0:11:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.24,0:11:09.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, look at that, amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.25,0:11:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They got a huge one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.33,0:11:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... a vessel from the guild?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.38,0:11:18.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You can feel the difference in funds\Nin your bones.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.09,0:11:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... I wish our ship was as big as\Nthat one...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.64,0:11:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.60,0:11:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.85,0:11:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The value of a ship isn't\Nmeasured by its size!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.23,0:11:33.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.40,0:11:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going back to the captain's cabin!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.53,0:11:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You both know that you can't badmouth\Nour Quin Zaza in front of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.82,0:11:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.32,0:11:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If I could, I'd like to dock the Zaza
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.24,0:11:49.16,Default,,0,0,0,,and overhaul its engine and stuff, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.29,0:11:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The frontal aileron tends to give me problems\Nlately too...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.67,0:11:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if its chain has become loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.79,0:11:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to check the steering system\Nthoroughly to...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.00,0:12:00.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... why this again...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.59,0:12:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We finally got some time off and\Nwe can't stop talking about work.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.59,0:12:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,With our lifestyle, there's not many\Ninteresting things to talk about...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.68,0:12:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Vannie... how about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.18,0:12:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh? How about what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.81,0:12:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,"What?", don't play dumb!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.69,0:12:18.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Being as popular as you are,\Nyou're sure to have plenty of partners to choose from!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.15,0:12:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm... not particularly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.57,0:12:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like she's not really interested in this...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.99,0:12:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,To the point it's actually endearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.49,0:12:27.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.20,0:12:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This round is a treat from the clients\Nover there...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.04,0:12:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.00,0:12:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.71,0:12:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhh... not my type at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.79,0:12:38.21,Default,,0,0,0,,They seem like trouble...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.34,0:12:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We'd rather not, thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.30,0:12:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.76,0:12:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.72,0:12:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...? What the fuck's your problem?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.09,0:12:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Our drinks are as good as any other!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.89,0:12:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.10,0:12:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't drink anything I haven't paid\Nfor myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.76,0:12:53.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh... we have an stuck-up lady right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.27,0:12:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Annoying men aren't precisely\Npopular anywhere, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.52,0:12:57.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But I like my women feisty like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.86,0:13:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They're at it again...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.44,0:13:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, wait, don't make a man\Nlose face like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.45,0:13:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.74,0:13:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want to have a drinking contest\NI wouldn't mind to oblige.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.91,0:13:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Mmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.33,0:13:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,About the loser's penalty,\Nlet's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.66,0:13:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How about paying for all the rounds\Nof everyone present in this lovely tavern?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.12,0:13:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.79,0:13:21.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.88,0:13:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like you have the guts, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.01,0:13:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We accept the challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.67,0:13:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,-Ahhh...\N-That's our girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.80,0:13:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Vannie-san...\NWill you be ok after saying that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.18,0:13:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew! I'm falling for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.31,0:13:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.73,0:13:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.27,0:13:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh...? You are, like,\Npretty amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.90,0:13:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You're noticing that now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.66,0:13:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.70,0:13:50.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, why are you working in this kind\Nof place?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.57,0:13:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-Hey! Come over here!\N-Right away!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.58,0:13:56.41,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.54,0:13:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that long face for, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.71,0:13:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Niko...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.92,0:14:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,If you find any girl to your liking\Ndon't be shy and invite her to a room!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.05,0:14:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... nah, I'm good.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.76,0:14:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just here because you guys dragged me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.18,0:14:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.43,0:14:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I can see from a mile away that if I did\Nanything I'd end up becoming the butt of the joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.89,0:14:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You know I think of you as you\Nwere my cute little brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.27,0:14:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But man, rubble like us...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.98,0:14:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't say when we will\Nhave another chance like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.69,0:14:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.24,0:14:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of me, brute!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.24,0:14:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, put her down! That girl\Nisn't taking any customers yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.24,0:14:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,No way, I want her and her alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.83,0:14:40.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you! What are you misunderstanding?\NLet me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.12,0:14:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She will end up taking customers\Nsooner or later.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.13,0:14:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,If that day is today, it doesn't\Nmatter, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.21,0:14:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That uniform... he is a member\Nof a ship crew too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.22,0:14:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Jiro, leave them alone.\NIt's better if we don't put ourselves in troubl-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.01,0:14:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you! Put her down!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.05,0:14:54.18,Default,,0,0,0,,-Oh...\N-Can't you see that she dislikes it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.01,0:14:57.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You... are you a draker?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.27,0:15:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. We just hunted a huge\Ndragon too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.98,0:15:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,As a draker, too, I'd rather not\Nsee something that does our name dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.48,0:15:07.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But this place is precisely where\Nthings get pretty dirty, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.40,0:15:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Can't you put me down before your\Nlittle conversation?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.36,0:15:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.32,0:15:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.20,0:15:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.08,0:15:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,-Quick, go upstairs and...\N-Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.29,0:15:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.54,0:15:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,This little pipsqueak says he's a draker!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.04,0:15:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.13,0:15:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of people like you that\Ndrakers get scorned everywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.38,0:15:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.46,0:15:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.88,0:15:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.43,0:15:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.97,0:15:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.22,0:15:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,-Mmm?\N-Ah?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.35,0:15:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.56,0:15:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, I'm sorry...\NYou see, I can't find my footing sometimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.02,0:15:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Niko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.27,0:15:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you be so kind\Nas to not pick on my little brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.40,0:15:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh??
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.36,0:15:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you picking a fight with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.19,0:15:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,What seems to be the problem?\NCan't take it easy like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.53,0:15:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,If you are going to fight,\Ndo it outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.49,0:15:55.78,Default,,0,0,0,,They're gonna fight, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.03,0:15:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.24,0:15:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.62,0:16:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, I can't control\Nmy hands too sometimes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.37,0:16:06.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh, how amusing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.25,0:16:07.09,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.38,0:16:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.59,0:16:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.92,0:16:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... what the hell were they thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.22,0:16:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You sure you don't need to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.89,0:16:19.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll pass.\NI'm a firm pacifist.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.81,0:16:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.77,0:16:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.73,0:16:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... This has become a whole mess...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.40,0:16:26.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... my precious bar...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.11,0:16:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,-Now's our chance!\N-Oh? Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.11,0:16:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.49,0:16:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This lady is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.54,0:16:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.75,0:16:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I... I give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.12,0:16:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That's our Vannie!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.37,0:16:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,She drank everything without\Nbreaking a sweat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.47,0:16:55.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The stalls are already in place!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.43,0:16:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,The day after tomorrow,\Nthere's going to be an annual festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.51,0:17:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You! What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.81,0:17:02.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Jiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.18,0:17:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,My name's Katja.\NThank you for earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.40,0:17:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,All that running made me hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.27,0:17:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,"Dragon meat hand-rolled Laghman"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.82,0:17:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I like mine with plenty of\Nsmashed peanuts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.49,0:17:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, can we eat this over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.66,0:17:20.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, as long as you return the plate.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.91,0:17:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.33,0:17:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.83,0:17:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.12,0:17:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? It's delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.79,0:17:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You were right, the more peanuts,\Nthe better!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.92,0:17:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Right? Enjoy it thoroughly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.38,0:17:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I say that, but you were the\None who paid for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.55,0:17:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh... so you guys travel around the\Nworld searching for dragons...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.31,0:17:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.64,0:17:48.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe this meat is from one of the\Ndragons you caught, eh, Jiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.44,0:17:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.23,0:17:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.07,0:17:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Tell me stories about the sky!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.32,0:17:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.16,0:18:03.41,Default,,0,0,0,,My father was a draker as well...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.54,0:18:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,And when I was a kid, he used to\Ntell me a lot of stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.50,0:18:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I see, I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.54,0:18:11.42,Default,,0,0,0,,So, in our ship there's this guy\Nnamed Mika who is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.96,0:18:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But, when I'm not there to look after\Nhim, he always end up doing something reckless!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.84,0:18:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.38,0:18:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.64,0:18:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wait a moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.18,0:18:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,-Here!\N-Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.64,0:18:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It sounds nice...\NWaking up and being over the clouds...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.73,0:18:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, life in the sky isn't so easy...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.36,0:18:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never set a foot out of this\Ncity in all my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.03,0:18:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Since they sold me when I was little\NI've been here, always.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.91,0:18:44.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it ridiculous?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.49,0:18:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though we're in a port city,\NI've never been to anywhere else.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.67,0:18:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time I go back...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.84,0:18:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for accompanying me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.97,0:19:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I only ever saw the festival\Nfrom my window.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.47,0:19:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It was pretty fun to have\Na little taste of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.14,0:19:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.93,0:19:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, see you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.73,0:19:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.56,0:19:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The day after tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.48,0:19:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's come here together!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.33,0:19:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.63,0:19:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.13,0:19:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys, I'm beyond tired of this bullshit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.67,0:19:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Each and every one of you, what the\Nfuck were you thinking, bunch of brainless monkeys?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.26,0:19:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope the brainless monkeys reflect\Non what they did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.72,0:19:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Soraya...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.01,0:19:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You were there and did nothing to stop them,\Nyou're just as guilty!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.89,0:19:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh! No way in hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.89,0:19:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Jiro! Where have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.52,0:19:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,To begin with, this was all because you did...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.86,0:19:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.82,0:20:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah? What's his problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.03,0:20:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened, guys?\NYou look totally wrecked.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.99,0:20:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,These are our proud medals as men.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.12,0:20:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Woah... it looks painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.04,0:20:13.00,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.54,0:20:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this seat free?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.83,0:20:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... Vannie...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.00,0:20:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been out heavy drinking again, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.17,0:20:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a tiny bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.84,0:20:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And that's why I need to cool off.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.51,0:20:28.89,Default,,0,0,0,,-Vannie...\N-Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.60,0:20:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, I...
